CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, May 12, 1956, pg. A30, reads: "Ideal School Winners - Winners in student model group from the Ideal School of Beauty Culture, at the Trade Show given by Pennsylvania Beauticians at the Fort Pitt Hotel, were Mrs .Velma Bowe, first; Charles Jones, third, and Wilma Bivins, second (left to right). -Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Student model winners from Ideal School of Beauty and Culture, from left: Velma Bowe, Charles Jones, and Wilma Bivins, posed in Fort Pitt Hotel during Pennsylvania Beauticians Trade Show
